From 8fd7a39d741bcbcb189970e7e15cb7ae23ba3455 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: mainframe98 <k.s.werf@hotmail.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Oct 2025 18:45:51 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 42/50] Regenerate symbol-information.json with a new script

Summary:
This script uses the underlying compatibility database that the
package used by the original script used. Rather than go through
the effort of installing it through composer, just download the
source directly and analyse the json files it provides. This
makes running the script really simple, and because no external
PHP code is executed, a lot safer.

In anticipation for traits and enums introduced in newer versions,
these have been added to the symbol-information.json file.
The compatibility database also records class constants, similar
to methods. These have also been added.

Closes T16274

Test Plan:
* Run rebuild-symbol-information.php
* Browse through a decade's worth of changes
* Despair at reviewing the changes (optional)

Reviewers: O1 Blessed Committers, avivey

Reviewed By: O1 Blessed Committers, avivey

Subscribers: avivey, tobiaswiese, valerio.bozzolan, Matthew, Cigaryno

Maniphest Tasks: T16274

Differential Revision: https://we.phorge.it/D26448
